{"type": "article", "id": 37029, "title": "时尚类产品去年卖得不好，以及，Lemaire的秋冬男装很潇洒 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-01-20T03:01:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 3203, "name": "Balenciaga"}, {"id": 3340, "name": "Valentino"}, {"id": 7469, "name": "Lemaire"}, {"id": 8634, "name": "Supreme"}, {"id": 36914, "name": "2017 秋冬男装"}, {"id": 4915, "name": "欧舒丹"}, {"id": 7973, "name": "Inditex"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 54, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170120103958lXYxwUfa2IE68Lj7.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/business-features/global-apparel-footwear-1-7t-industry-in-2016-10757713/\" rel=\"nofollow\">2016 年，全球服饰及鞋类市场</a>增长缓滞</b>｜据 wwd 报道，2016 年的全球服饰及鞋类市场，达到了 1.7 万亿美元。实现了 3.8% 的增长。这是继 2008 年之后，增长幅度最小的一年。</p><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://globalcosmeticsnews.com/europe/3892/l-occitane-announces-disposal-of-le-couvent-des-minimes-to-hld-group\" rel=\"nofollow\">法国欧舒丹集团出售旗下古龙水及天然护肤品牌</a></b> | 法国欧舒丹集团（L’Occitane）近日宣布，已将旗下的古龙水和天然护肤品牌 Le Couvent des Minimes 出售给由法国投资集团 HLD 与法国医学护肤品牌 Filorga 、SVR的股东共同组成的投资集团。Le Couvent des Minimes 品牌于 2004 年在欧舒丹集团内部创立，主要销售古龙水及身体护肤品，据称年营收近 1000 万欧元。欧舒丹集团 CEO Reinold Geiger 说，该交易将使得公司专注于最重要的核心品牌。<br></p><p><a href=\"https://fashionunited.uk/news/business/would-inditex-s-lefties-take-on-h-m-and-primark-in-2017/2017011823200\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Inditex 旗下又一个品牌要进入美国市场</b></a> | Zara 的母公司 Inditex 宣布，旗下的 Lefties 品牌要扩张国际市场，从欧洲进入美国。这个品牌 1993 年建立，之前给人的印象是以低价售卖 Zara 的库存货，但后来建立了自己的产品线，强调“低价的独立品牌”。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>当地时间 1 月 19 日，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/nike-miami-first-look\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike 全新迈阿密旗舰店正式开业</a>，该店占地共 31000 平方英尺，设有两层购物空间。店内除了贩售 Nike 各大支线的最新设计外，更设有专门的 Nike Basketball, Nike Soccer 和 Nike Running 体验区，顾客可以提前预约专业的 Nike 运动指导服务。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120104024jFhx6ostNTPXGidM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120104026umGMOndvhebXJq5w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120104027nvmAOCdIuYPoex9E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120104027kxY6o8249P0ZguHi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120104028QYGD8iIyRreu3wJf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120104027FAKgMh90Um34QVqu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120104038xcpojPm8lCG1KLkR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120104038UE570ziTmGLW82Nc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120104047OniZ3GUWJ641cDwF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120104047pRSMkf1zhoTcnl7B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">各大品牌纷纷发布 2017 秋冬男装系列，“年轻化”，似乎是它们想要传达的共同主题：</p><p><font color=\"#333332\" size=\"4\">简约系的法国品牌 Lemaire，在 2017 秋冬系列中，似乎色彩选择变得更开放了。</font>湖绿、芥末黄、橄榄绿、深红、宝蓝等色调的出现，丰富了 Lemaire 先前的黑白设定。更低廓形结合精选的面料，则延续了 Lemaire 一贯的优雅。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017012010275092EDGmtS1VcXh6jd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102750sbRjn3AoJUWt2k6L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102750beV7W3sDiPwxcpov.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102805349KRfryH5oUOWZ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102805H0nGlbpsceivTMj3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701201028053LaVfwX70nemSuGl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102805K6pZqHtCcUdFDhgw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102805h39RswqdWDOoHJM7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102805OEWLvVnAbqIDg6ks.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102806kBbZ2TvrageNWXHl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701201028062labdOJExzZqjNmy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102806Er3S9G7KJyDOMs2Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>在 LV 2017 秋冬男装系列的秀场上，LV 与 Supreme 的联名款正式发布。该系列融合了 Louis Vuitton 经典的 Monogram 图案与 Supreme 签名式的 Box Logo，以各自标志性的红色和棕色呈现，带来了包括背包、旅行袋、邮差包、腰包、收纳包和钱包等包袋以及衬衫、围巾、钥匙圈、手套等多款配件。另外还有定制 Trunk 旅行箱以及滑板，以红白二色的  Monogram 图案作装饰。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102837ho5belzXC60WPdIy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102837Tw160rHLjZP4hoJz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102837rysDVOhpjGPF4m9o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102838juoK8PQDBHcTeMxW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102838PSk8ZrU6OcDWls4a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701201028381oX0psbOVta9jgNT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102838ha8D5EWjcQd2JeNs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701201028381bsREBkIOvtwVLFK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102838Z9npXvAqwC28BfdI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701201028388jg5ixEwlkDsWzVU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102839dMLfsHGqwR5plxoY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102839lbBcjhpIuknmt5Xr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102857BihuEZW5eMDacQCN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102925RtlbYxsrEne8I4p9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102926U5fBCipLl0DxWt4n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102935bGVwCiOpUdcehK0E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017012010293532i7yCGeLYvUmXkb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Pierpaolo Piccioli 的 Valentino 首秀，带来了 2017 男装秋冬系列。这场秀似乎想强调“街头风”，其秀场上的每个模特都戴着棒球帽。Piccioli 更是特别邀请来英国艺术家 Jamie Reid 打造了「Beauty is a birthright, reclaim your heritage.」和「It seemed to be the end, until the next beginning.」两句短诗，出现在大衣和羊毛衫上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701201029576yBSPr9qGJDMcKTe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102957vawF1QCuXB9j7efy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120102958hBoRzQe9ryi86VGm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103001YEIvibQH7L9zTBpm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103001dvz7stRX5pcWe1rE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103001Mqap0e1gFvxJ9hIl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103005PYaJc6uEZT7iFbVR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103026IOFE5Av27CdNby8r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103026l32acTvVu5PF1Z96.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103026ieks1moJw2gBrV4j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701201030348xjh0yuWNLZoaswY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103034h2oEtHMOW4efqzTG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">在 2017 秋冬系列，Balenciaga 也变得更加年轻和街头化了：充满力量感的短身皮夹克，蓬松的羽绒外套和背心，连帽衫与格纹衬衫和卫衣的混搭，亮眼的围巾，购物袋一样的皮革手提包，拼接材质和前卫线条的 Triple-S 球鞋，也许就会成为下一个街头热点。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103057Z73LzF9EVMOhHNpI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103057X5GobTF0nSsKmfDV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103057yu3cvJLFNSEUB5Cf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103057lsq7gpic5bVGT43O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103057iXc64fS2rTwgZYuI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103057MDc6z4ugb9Sk70Io.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701201030576BcxO8S7fIsoNqj1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103057tsSCTQiB7NaYdJVl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103058qb0fezvgMh6TXKUR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103058mevPhGzHlj1Mk3Xa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701201030570rNGZSDUw3mofAQz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103058KnEjtz1OCpGZaYmJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103113aiT5x0b6H7CkEYML.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103113mNZVFzfRdHatnUrQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170120103113Pky4CF8wHSoiLJhn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/mens-fall-collections-2017/paris/louis-vuitton/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">wwd</a></p>"}